    {
      "id": "ex-li-1",
      "type": "listen",
      "skill": "listening",
      "prompt": "Listen to the union rep. What are they demanding?",
      "audio": "audio/b2.1/unit-10-contract-claims/listen-1.mp3",
      "transcript": "Nous exigeons que les heures supplémentaires soient payées ; sinon, la grève commencera lundi.",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "a",
          "text": "That overtime be paid — otherwise a strike starts Monday"
        },
        {
          "id": "b",
          "text": "That the strike end on Monday"
        },
        {
          "id": "c",
          "text": "That salaries be reduced"
        }
      ],
      "correct": [
        "a"
      ],
      "explanation": "« Nous exigeons que… soient payées » + the strike ultimatum."
    },
    {
      "id": "ex-rd-1",
      "type": "read",
      "skill": "reading",
      "prompt": "Read the staff-meeting account and answer both questions.",
      "passageFr": "La direction nous a présenté le nouveau contrat hier. Le syndicat tient à ce que les indemnités soient garanties par écrit : « Promettre ne suffit pas. Donnez-les-nous noir sur blanc », a déclaré la déléguée. En cas de refus, les salariés voteront la grève — le préavis serait déjà déposé, selon certains.",
      "passageEn": "Management presented the new contract to us yesterday. The union insists that the compensation be guaranteed in writing: \"Promising isn't enough. Give it to us in black and white,\" declared the rep. If refused, the employees will vote to strike — notice has reportedly already been filed, according to some.",
      "questions": [
        {
          "id": "q1",
          "prompt": "What does the union insist on?",
          "options": [
            {
              "id": "a",
              "text": "That compensation be guaranteed in writing"
            },
            {
              "id": "b",
              "text": "That the contract be cancelled entirely"
            },
            {
              "id": "c",
              "text": "That management resign"
            }
          ],
          "correct": [
            "a"
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "q2",
          "prompt": "« Le préavis serait déjà déposé » — why the conditional?",
          "options": [
            {
              "id": "a",
              "text": "It's an unconfirmed rumour"
            },
            {
              "id": "b",
              "text": "It's a polite request"
            },
            {
              "id": "c",
              "text": "It's a regret"
            }
          ],
          "correct": [
            "a"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex-mc-4",
      "type": "multiple-choice",
      "skill": "writing",
      "prompt": "Pick the correct stacked imperative for \"Talk to her about it\":",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "a",
          "text": "Parlez-lui-en."
        },
        {
          "id": "b",
          "text": "Parlez-en-lui."
        },
        {
          "id": "c",
          "text": "Lui en parlez."
        }
